{
  "stem": "13219.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I know that my father had papers to come to America because a cousin of his by the name of [INAUDIBLE] send him the papers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he never wanted to go by himself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he didn't have papers for the-- for us and, and, and my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he never went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the when, when that cousin, [INAUDIBLE], which he was a very successful businessman in America, was there for a few years, he did send them, I think, in 1920, '21.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he, he's supposed to go by himself and then bring, then bring the family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't think he wanted that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first sign is-- was 1939 in the, in the summer of 1939.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we were, we, we, we, we heard that Germany is, is-- took over Austria, took over Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they may, they may take over Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were way up north next to the Russian border, not far from Ukraine, which it was Russia at that time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw a lot of people, Jews, who flew-- who came back from, from south, like Warsaw and-- to, to, to up north.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we heard stories about killings and pogroms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you know, you always think that it's not going to happen to you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And till 1939, when they made up a pact with Germany and Russia, that Germany will take half of Poland and Russia will take half of Poland.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was under the Russian-- city came under the Russian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, frightened-- yes or no-- a little bit frightened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if you have, if you, you know, you were disturbed in your life, it's frightened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You thank God that you were under the Russian mandate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it won't be any killing [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
